 Pool, and only one was right.","id":"c3","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"leilani"},{"cat":"pool","value":"mistpool"},{"cat":"pool","value":"stonepool"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneOf","type":"oneOf"},{"clueText":"The one who wore the Cotton Robe was not 2 soaks.","id":"c4","operands":[{"cat":"soak","value":"soak2"},{"cat":"robe","value":"cottonrobe"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"It was Amara who took 6 soaks.","id":"c5","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"amara"},{"cat":"soak","value":"soak6"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"eq","type":"eq"},{"clueText":"Of Dmitri and Sofia, one sipped the coffee and the other sipped the warm milk.","id":"c6","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"dmitri"},{"cat":"bather","value":"sofia"},{"cat":"drink","value":"coffee"},{"cat":"drink","value":"milk"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneEachOf","type":"oneEachOf"},{"clueText":"If Sofia sipped the warm milk, then Leilani was not the one who wore the Cotton Robe.","id":"c7","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"sofia"},{"cat":"drink","value":"milk"},{"cat":"bather","value":"leilani"},{"cat":"robe","value":"cottonrobe"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"ifThen","type":"ifThen"},{"clueText":"The one who wore the Wool Robe was not the mineral-water sipper.","id":"c8","operands":[{"cat":"drink","value":"water"},{"cat":"robe","value":"woolrobe"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"The one who wore the Wool Robe was not the Cedar Pool regular.","id":"c9","operands":[{"cat":"pool","value":"cedarpool"},{"cat":"robe","value":"woolrobe"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"Of Dmitri and Kenji, one wore the Linen Robe and the other wore the Bamboo Robe.","id":"c10","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"dmitri"},{"cat":"bather","value":"kenji"},{"cat":"robe","value":"linenrobe"},{"cat":"robe","value":"bamboorobe"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneEachOf","type":"oneEachOf"},{"clueText":"For Kenji the ledger read Fruit juice or Coffee - just one was true.","id":"c11","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"kenji"},{"cat":"drink","value":"juice"},{"cat":"drink","value":"coffee"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneOf","type":"oneOf"},{"clueText":"Dmitri took 2 more soaks than Leilani did.","id":"c12","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"dmitri"},{"cat":"bather","value":"leilani"}],"params":{"delta":2,"dir":"greater","numericCat":"soak"},"renderHint":"numDiff","type":"numDiff"},{"clueText":"Noor was down to Wool Robe or Cotton Robe, and only one was right.","id":"c13","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"noor"},{"cat":"robe","value":"woolrobe"},{"cat":"robe","value":"cottonrobe"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneOf","type":"oneOf"},{"clueText":"It was not the green-tea sipper who wore the Silk Robe.","id":"c14","operands":[{"cat":"drink","value":"tea"},{"cat":"robe","value":"silkrobe"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"Of Dmitri and Kenji, one settled in the Stone Pool and the other settled in the Ember Pool.","id":"c15","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"dmitri"},{"cat":"bather","value":"kenji"},{"cat":"pool","value":"stonepool"},{"cat":"pool","value":"emberpool"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneEachOf","type":"oneEachOf"},{"clueText":"Dmitri was down to Coffee or Green tea, and only one was right.","id":"c16","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"dmitri"},{"cat":"drink","value":"coffee"},{"cat":"drink","value":"tea"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"oneOf","type":"oneOf"},{"clueText":"the fruit-juice sipper was not the one who took 12 soaks.","id":"c17","operands":[{"cat":"drink","value":"juice"},{"cat":"soak","value":"soak12"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"the coffee sipper was not the one who settled in the Ember Pool.","id":"c18","operands":[{"cat":"drink","value":"coffee"},{"cat":"pool","value":"emberpool"}],"params":{},"renderHint":"neq","type":"neq"},{"clueText":"It was Sofia who took 8 soaks.","id":"c19","operands":[{"cat":"bather","value":"sofia"},{"cat":"s